official_title: To direct the Secretary of the Interior to convey to the City of Imperial Beach, California, approximately 1 acre of land in the Tijuana Slough National Wildlife Refuge.

summary.text: Directs the Secretary of the Interior to convey to Imperial Beach, California, without compensation, specified land in the Tijuana Slough National Wildlife Refuge for use as a public recreational area.
